oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mountains near state line
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A view of the mountains in the distance on the Tennessee-North Carolina state line near Greeneville, Tenn. A farmland, with barn and fences, is in the foreground. Clouds appear above the mountains.
